channel.title: Since when do my clients not work?
channel.description:
Two days ago all my clients worked perfectly but now all of a sudden they just stopped working exact problem:
1. I extract the files 2. I try to run the Batch File in it 3. It goes like it normally would but instead of the actual client coming up nothing happens
Help!

item.title: Since when do my clients not work?
item.dc:creator: @Indentatus Indentatus
item.description:
@Indentatus wrote:

Huh you don’t have to restore it to anywhere haha

You go to Start>Programs>Accessories>System Tools>System Restore

Follow the instructions… like 3 clicks and u sit back and in 5 mins ull have ur comp restored! It does everything for you!

item.dc:creator: @Indentatus Indentatus
item.description:
@Indentatus wrote:

An easy fix that would 99% of the time fix it would be a little System Restore… restore to how many hours ago it wasnt working… REMEMBER that none of your files will disapear so your server files will be just fine:)

It’s probably just a small change in the system somewhere, restoring back a bit should fix it!

If not, hey, just unrestore!
